::Shredder::

Shredder looks over at Snare, frowning. "I know of a place to stay, but they 
might come after us. First we need to get repairs and such, and alert a few 
factions of them. It'd be good if they're fighting battles every day or so. 
Devensive ones I mean."

He changes course. "Let's stop by at the Cybertronian Fire and get repaired."
